You can take the man out of Barcelona, but you can never take the Barcelona out of the man.

That phrase is certainly true for Bayern Munich boss Pep Guardiola who celebrated with the home fans as Ivan Rakitic opened the scoring for Barcelona against Manchester City.

Guardiola quickly stemmed his excitement by covering his face with his scalf as he realised he was celebrating in front of the world's media. 

