The Catalan side went on to beat Manuel Pellegrini's side 1-0 as they progressed to the last eight of the Champions League.

Guardiola knows all about life at the club having managed there between 2008 and 2012, and their progression now means he could end up facing his former employers in the next round of the Champions League.

Bayern Munich themselves cantered through with ease as they thumped Shakhtar Donetsk 7-0 at the Allianz Arena following a goalless first leg against the Ukranian side. 

